---
// ChampionKit.astro — email CTA for the briefing document
---

<div class="py-12 px-8 border border-[#1e293b] rounded-sm">
  <p class="label mb-4">Champion Kit</p>
  <h2 class="text-headline font-light mb-3">Make the case internally.</h2>
  <p class="text-body text-[#94a3b8] mb-8 max-w-lg">
    A 3-page briefing document to help you make the case internally — covering who Azeem is, what a session looks like, and the strategic questions it addresses.
  </p>

  <form
    class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 max-w-md"
    onsubmit="return false;"
    aria-label="Request Champion Kit"
  >
    <label for="ck-email" class="sr-only">Your work email</label>
    <input
      id="ck-email"
      type="email"
      placeholder="Your work email"
      autocomplete="email"
      required
      class="flex-1 bg-[#0f172a] border border-[#334155] text-[#f1f5f9] placeholder-[#475569]
             px-4 py-3 text-sm rounded-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-[#64748b] transition-colors"
    />
    <button
      type="submit"
      class="btn-primary whitespace-nowrap px-6 py-3 text-sm"
    >
      Send me the kit
    </button>
  </form>

  <p class="text-caption text-[#475569] mt-4">
    No spam. One email with the document attached.
  </p>
</div>
